::Prowl::

Prowl looks down at Iron Raptor with a bit of surprise as she speaks, 
something telling him that whatever had happened to her has passed.

"I don't know, love," he says, "You seem to have gotten a new beast 
mode though. We'll get you checked out at the lab after we get you 
repaired at the CR."

They reach the CR room, the doors opening to let them through.


--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, "Megan Solmonson" <tmrattrap@h...> wrote:
> 
> * She was way too tired now, and she was experiencing enough pain 
that her 
> total logic could resurface any moment.
> But until then she just wanted to lay down, close her eyes and 
drift off to 
> sleep. Where there was no pain ever.
> 
> With Prowls hand on her neck she felt slightly comforted, her 
memories 
> telling her of varied occasions of when she had been held in his 
arms.
> Huh? She actually remembered that?
> It was then that her programming suddenly came to the basic truth, 
when her 
> logic pushed back the beast modes and she actually was able to 
think 
> clearly.
> 
> With a snarl of shock she rose to her hind legs almost as if she 
had 
> suddenly woken up from a horrable dream!
> Her head snapped in every direction until her eyes fell on 
Prowl...and his 
> damage.
> She was just about to ask him just what had happened when she 
looked 
> down...and saw her hands.
> She almost jumped back in complete surprise.*
> 
> " W...what.....?"
> 
> * She looked back up at Prowl with an expression which relayed her 
> confusion.*
> 
> " What's happened to me?!!"
